#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn7.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Upāsakavagga "
msgstr "2. Lay Followers "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Mānatthaddhasutta "
msgstr "15. Stuck-Up "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.178, pts2ed1.382, sc1
msgctxt "sn7.15:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena mānatthaddho nāma brāhmaṇo sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati. "
msgstr "Now at that time a brahmin named Stuck-Up was residing in Sāvatthī. "

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.3"
msgid "So neva mātaraṃ abhivādeti, na pitaraṃ abhivādeti, na ācariyaṃ abhivādeti, na jeṭṭhabhātaraṃ abhivādeti. "
msgstr "He didn’t bow to his mother or father, his teacher, or his oldest brother. "

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.4"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā mahatiyā parisāya parivuto dhammaṃ deseti. "
msgstr "Now, at that time the Buddha was teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:1.5"
msgid "Atha kho mānatthaddhassa brāhmaṇassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Stuck-Up thought, "

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.6"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho samaṇo gotamo mahatiyā parisāya parivuto dhammaṃ deseti. "
msgstr "“The ascetic Gotama is teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly. "

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.7"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ. "
msgstr "Why don’t I approach him? "

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.8"
msgid "Sace maṃ samaṇo gotamo ālapissati, ahampi taṃ ālapissāmi. "
msgstr "If he speaks to me, I’ll speak to him. "

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.9"
msgid "No ce maṃ samaṇo gotamo ālapissati, ahampi nālapissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "But if he doesn’t speak, neither will I.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:1.10"
msgid "Atha kho mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā tuṇhībhūto ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
msgstr "Then the brahmin Stuck-Up went up to the Buddha, and stood silently to one side. "

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.11"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā taṃ nālapi. "
msgstr "But the Buddha didn’t speak to him. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:1.12"
msgid "Atha kho mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo: "
msgstr "Then Stuck-Up thought, "

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.13"
msgid "“nāyaṃ samaṇo gotamo kiñci jānātī”ti tatova puna nivattitukāmo ahosi. "
msgstr "“This ascetic Gotama knows nothing!” And he wanted to go back from there right away. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:1.14"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā mānatthaddhassa brāhmaṇassa cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya mānatthaddhaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha, knowing what Stuck-Up was thinking, addressed him in verse: "

# NOTE: See BB for reading.
#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn7.15:2.1"
msgid "“Na mānaṃ brāhmaṇa sādhu, "
msgstr "“It’s not good to foster conceit "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:2.2"
msgid "atthikassīdha brāhmaṇa; "
msgstr "if you want what’s good for you, brahmin. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:2.3"
msgid "Yena atthena āgacchi, "
msgstr "You should foster the goal "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:2.4"
msgid "tamevamanubrūhaye”ti. "
msgstr "which brought you here.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.383, sc3
msgctxt "sn7.15:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo: "
msgstr "Then Stuck-Up thought,"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.2"
msgid "“cittaṃ me samaṇo gotamo jānātī”ti tattheva bhagavato pādesu sirasā nipatitvā bhagavato pādāni mukhena ca paricumbati pāṇīhi ca parisambāhati, nāmañca sāveti: "
msgstr "“The ascetic Gotama knows my mind!” He bowed with his head to the Buddha’s feet, caressing them and covering them with kisses, and pronounced his name:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.3"
msgid "“mānatthaddhāhaṃ, bho gotama, mānatthaddhāhaṃ, bho gotamā”ti. "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, I am Stuck-Up! I am Stuck-Up!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: abbhutavittajātā → abbhutacittajātā (bj, km, pts1-2) | abbhūtacittajātā (s1-3) | acchariyabbhutacittajātā (mr)
msgctxt "sn7.15:3.4"
msgid "Atha kho sā parisā abbhutavittajātā ahosi: "
msgstr "Then that assembly was stunned:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.5"
msgid "“acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho. "
msgstr "“It’s incredible, it’s amazing! "

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.6"
msgid "Ayañhi mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo neva mātaraṃ abhivādeti, na pitaraṃ abhivādeti, na ācariyaṃ abhivādeti, na jeṭṭhabhātaraṃ abhivādeti; "
msgstr "This brahmin Stuck-Up doesn’t bow to his mother or father, his teacher, or his oldest brother. "

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.7"
msgid "atha ca pana samaṇe gotame evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karotī”ti. "
msgstr "Yet he shows such utmost devotion to the ascetic Gotama!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:3.8"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā mānatthaddhaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to the brahmin Stuck-Up,"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.9"
msgid "“alaṃ, brāhmaṇa, uṭṭhehi, sake āsane nisīda. "
msgstr "“Enough, brahmin. Get up, and take your own seat. "

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.10"
msgid "Yato te mayi cittaṃ pasannan”ti. "
msgstr "For your mind has confidence in me.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:3.11"
msgid "Atha kho mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo sake āsane nisīditvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Stuck-Up took his seat and said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.384, sc4
msgctxt "sn7.15:4.1"
msgid "“Kesu na mānaṃ kayirātha, "
msgstr "“Regarding whom should you not be conceited? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:4.2"
msgid "kesu cassa sagāravo; "
msgstr "Who should you respect? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:4.3"
msgid "Kyassa apacitā assu, "
msgstr "Who should you esteem? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:4.4"
msgid "kyassu sādhu supūjitā”ti. "
msgstr "Who is it good to venerate properly?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.1"
msgid "“Mātari pitari cāpi, "
msgstr "“Your mother and father, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.2"
msgid "atho jeṭṭhamhi bhātari; "
msgstr "and also your oldest brother, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.3"
msgid "Ācariye catutthamhi, "
msgstr "with teacher as fourth. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.4"
msgid "tesu na mānaṃ kayirātha; "
msgstr "Regarding these you should not be conceited. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.5"
msgid "Tesu assa sagāravo, "
msgstr "They are who you should respect. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.6"
msgid "tyassa apacitā assu; "
msgstr "They are who you should esteem. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.7"
msgid "Tyassu sādhu supūjitā. "
msgstr "And they’re who it’s good to venerate properly. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn7.15:6.1"
msgid "Arahante sītībhūte, "
msgstr "And when you’ve humbled conceit, and aren’t stuck-up, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:6.2"
msgid "katakicce anāsave; "
msgstr "show supreme reverence for "

# NOTE: nihacca, though given in the dicts as “destroy, strike down”, is only used in contexts of conceit, or “bending the knee” to bow. It thus seems to have a more specific nuance.
#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:6.3"
msgid "Nihacca mānaṃ athaddho, "
msgstr "the perfected ones, cooled, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:6.4"
msgid "te namasse anuttare”ti. "
msgstr "their task complete, free of defilements.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.385, sc7
msgctxt "sn7.15:7.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin Stuck-Up said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn7.15:7.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama … "

msgctxt "sn7.15:7.3"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
